6. Program Menu:
================

LoadLibrary has a pulldown menu with shortcuts for a most USER-friendly
toolhandling.

	 		 @{" Load...            L " Link "Load"}
			 @{" LibVersion...      V " Link "LibVersion"}
			 @{" Remove only...     O " Link "Remove only"}
			 @{" Help...            H " Link "Helping"}
			 @{" About...           ? " Link "About"}
			 @{" Remove and Quit... R " Link "Remove and Quit"}
			 @{" Quit...            Q " Link "Quit"}

@EndNode

@Node "Load" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/Load"
@Next "LibVersion"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 Load..........-» This opens the 'REQTOOLS' filerequester in which you can
		  select the  library  you want to load. Any other kind of
		  files will simply be refused. You can also load a couple
		  of libraries with MultiSelection. You only have to press
		  the <SHIFT> Key during File-Selection.
@EndNode


@Node "LibVersion" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/LibVersion"
@Next "About"
@Prev "Load"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 LibVersion....-» Opens the filerequester from 'reqtools.library' in which
		  you can select the library you want to have a look at.
@EndNode


@Node "About" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/About"
@Next "Remove only"
@Prev "LibVersion"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 About.........-» This opens a little window with some informations about
		  the CopyRight, Author, Version you are using, and how
		  many libraries you have installed since then. Just
		  click on the gadget or press return to get rid of it.
@EndNode


@Node "Remove only" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/Remove only"
@Next "Quit"
@Prev "About"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 Remove only...-» Will remove ALL libraries loaded with LoadLibrary.
		  But not the CLI/SHELL loaded ones!!!
@EndNode


@Node "Quit" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/Quit"
@Next "Helping"
@Prev "Remove only"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 Quit..........-» This will quit the program without removing the loaded
		  libraries after asking for confirmation.
@EndNode


@Node "Helping" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/Help"
@Next "Remove and Quit"
@Prev "Quit"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 Help..........-» This nifty textfile Holger made for us.

@EndNode


@Node "Remove and Quit" "LoadLibrary.guide/Programm Menu/Remove and Quit"
@Prev "Helping"
@Toc "Program Menu"

 Remove and Quit » First, LoadLibrary will remove ALL loaded libraries.
		   Then it will simply quit the tool after asking for
		   confirmation.

@EndNode


