7.1 Know Bugs:
==============

 Do not install libraries which are in different directories with the 
 multiselection.

 -DH0:
 |___Libs:#?.library			; normal.
     |___OtherLibs:#?.library		; abnormal.

 If LoadLibrary try to install the libraries in 'Libs' AND 'OtherLibs', it
 will simply crash. Please,install one path after another. The other thing
 isn't a real bug, but you should know. You can only write in lower-case.
 OpenLibrary() will only accept correct Filehandling.
@EndNode

